[{'degrees': ['Bachelor, Industrial engineering & management, Studied in Amsterdam, the Netherlands.0'], 'end': '2012', 'start': '2009', 'education_org': 'Hogeschool van Amsterdam', 'summary': 'Industrial engineering is a branch of engineering dealing with the optimization of complex processes or systems. It is concerned with the development, improvement, implementation and evaluation of integrated systems of people, money, knowledge, information, equipment, energy, materials, analysis and synthesis, as well as the mathematical, physical and social sciences together with the principles and methods of engineering design to specify, predict, and evaluate the results to be obtained from such systems or processes. Its underlying concepts overlap considerably with certain business-oriented disciplines such as operations management, but the engineering side tends to emphasize extensive mathematical proficiency and usage of quantitative methods.'}, {'degrees': ['1e, Marcom A'], 'end': '2011', 'start': '2011', 'education_org': 'Agentschap Telecom', 'summary': 'People using maritime radio equipment on board of ships. Depending on the communication equipment with which the ship is equipped, it is a necessity that these people own a Marcom A Certificate, handed out by the Telecom Agency.

 Contents
 This course works on the maritime radio communication equipment, as described in the Global Maritime Distress and Safety System when in Sea Area A1 t/m A4 such as: VHF, MF, Sart, Navtex, hand radio, satellite communication equipment, SATCOM A,B,C. The exam consists of: procedures / technique / geography / English and (practical) operational skills. To be able to make the prescribed radio connections in case of nautical, public, emergency – distress – and safety communication, we work with real communication systems and / or interactive simulation.'}, {'degrees': ['1e, Green Belt, Amsterdam, the Netherlands'], 'end': '2011', 'start': '2011', 'education_org': 'UNC Lean sixsigma', 'summary': 'Lean Six Sigma (LSS) is a performance improvement philosophy, methodology and toolset in one. It has become a commonly used approach to performance improvement projects. The benefits of LSS are focus on customer requirements and process efficiency and the fact that decisions are based on data. The outcome is improved customer satisfaction and significant cost reduction. While the structured approach and data based decision making ensure tight project control. LSS helps mobilising the professionals in an organisation for a focused continuous improvement journey, improving employee effectiveness and providing a performance oriented culture.
 Green Belts play a very important role in larger performance improvement projects taking upon them specific tasks or responsibilities.'}, {'degrees': ['1e, CI-5B, Ioniserende Straling'], 'end': '2011', 'start': '2010', 'education_org': 'Elsevier icm Applus RTD', 'summary': "I used this education during my work as NORM/LSA focal point. NORM means Natural Occuring Radioactive Material and LSA means Lage Specifieke Activiteit.
 Thema's/Vakken
 - Werken met open radioactieve bronnen
 - Radionuclidenlaboratoria
 - Omgaan met natuurlijke radionucliden
 - Contaminatie en decontaminatie
 - Vervoer van radioactieve bronnen
 - Inwendige besmetting
 - Kernenergiewetdossier en nieuwe ontwikkelingen"}, {'degrees': ['1e, HMI / OIM Training, Heeze, the Netherlands'], 'end': '2010', 'start': '2010', 'education_org': 'Advisafe trainingen', 'summary': 'HMI or OIM means Hoofd Mijnbouw Installatie or Offshore Installation Manager.
 The course is designed for personnel that have some experience in the role of OIM or as part of the control team during emergencies and are seeking refinement in their emergency leadership role and validation assessment of their skills in this area.
 Objective:
 The purpose of this course is to enable prospective and incumbent candidates for the position of OIM or Deputy to implement and practice the procedures required to manage emergencies that may be encountered on an offshore platform and drill rig.'}, {'degrees': ['NVQ3, Oil and gas production Technology, studied in Aberdeen, Scotland UK'], 'end': '2008', 'start': '2007', 'education_org': 'ASET Skills development specialst', 'summary': 'It is designed to assess persons who are involved with the use and safety of refinery, processing systems and associated equipment used on offshore rigs.
 At Level 3, this award is aimed at those candidates who have additional, or specialist skills and knowledge of the petroleum production processing areas and finished the level 2 degree. It
 will also allow them to take a greater degree of responsibility.
 The demand for skilled and knowledgeable personnel in this field is increasing and it provides a progression route for candidates who already work and operate within the plant.'}, {'degrees': ['NVQ 2 City & Guilds, Oil and Gas production technology, studied in Aberdeen, Scotland UK'], 'end': '2007', 'start': '2006', 'education_org': 'ASET Skills development specialst', 'summary': 'It is designed to assess persons who are involved with the use and safety of refinery, processing systems and associated equipment used on offshore rigs.
 At Level 2, this award is aimed at those candidates who have followed all of the theory and finished/passed the exams and tests given during the theory sessions.'}, {'degrees': ['Secondary technical school, level 4., Process & Environment technology, Studied in Groningen, the Netherlands'], 'end': '2003', 'start': '2002', 'education_org': 'Alfa College', 'summary': 'De studie Process & environment technology is opgezet door de VAPRO (vakopleiding procesindustrie) en wordt ook wel VAPRO C genoemd.
 Procestechniek is het deel van de techniek dat zich bezig houdt met het ontwerp en de bedrijfsvoering alsmede de bediening, van installaties uit de procesindustrie. Dit vakgebied bestaat uit een deel werktuigbouwkunde, elektrotechniek en chemie, en heeft doorgaans een hoop te doen met regeltechniek.
 De automatisering van procestechniek kan met verschillende systemen worden aangepakt, de definities van de termen overlappen elkaar gedeeltelijk, de volgorde is over het algemeen van eenvoudig naar complex:
 Programmable logic controller (PLC)
 SCADA
 Distributed control system (DCS)
 Process control system (PCS).'}, {'degrees': ['Secondary technical school, level 4, Oil & Gas Treating and Maintenance Technology, Studied in Den Helder, the Netherlands'], 'end': '2002', 'start': '2001', 'education_org': 'ROC kop van Noord-Holland', 'summary': 'De Nederlandse bodem en zee bevat grote delen waar zich gas en olie bevindt. Het winnen van gas en olie gebeurt door middel van speciale machines en installaties, bijvoorbeeld dieselmotoren, pompen, compressoren en boordraaitafels. De Petroleum Gas –en onderhoudstecnicus houdt zich bezig met het bedienen, onderhouden en rapareren van dit soort machines. Tijdens de opleiding leer je een aantal technieken die nodig zijn om petroleum- en gasinstallaties te onderhouden, zoals Verspanen en Onderhoudstechniek Olie/Gas. Daarnaast leer je de machines en installaties te bedienen. Ook leer je over de chemische eigenschappen van stoffen en veiligheidsregelingen. Veiligheid is erg belangrijk in dit werk.
 Taken: De Petroleum Gas- en Onderhoudstechnicus houdt zich bezig met het controleren, beheren, repareren en onderhouden van installaties. Je werkzaamheden voer je vaak buiteneuit, weer of geen weer. Ook werk je vaak op zee, op een boorplatform.'}, {'degrees': ['Secondary technical school, level4, Mechanical engineering, Studied in Leeuwarden, the Netherlands'], 'end': '2001', 'start': '1997', 'education_org': 'Friesland College', 'summary': 'Werktuigbouwkunde of werktuigkunde is een technische studie waarin het ontwerpen van dynamische objecten wordt bijgebracht. De werktuigbouwkunde wordt daarbij opgesplitst in een aantal deelgebieden, deze zijn: machinebouw, scheepsbouw, offshore, olie- en gaswinning, onderzoek en toepassing, energie- en aandrijftechniek, staal- en constructiebouw. In de werktuigbouwkunde worden in deze sectoren objecten ontworpen die handelingen moeten uitvoeren, zoals tillen, wegen, verplaatsen, druk opbouwen, analyseren, warmte wisselen, verbinden of verspanen. Ook de produceerbaarheid van de objecten behoort tot de werktuigbouwkunde.
 Bij elk product dat op de markt verschijnt, is een werktuigbouwkundige betrokken. Die ontwerpt en construeert machines om die nieuwe producten te maken. Als werktuigbouwkundige ben je verantwoordelijk voor het totale werkproces. Jij bent degene die overlegt met de opdrachtgever, de werkplaatschefs en leveranciers.'}, {'degrees': ['Secondary modern level D, High school, Midsland, the Netherlands'], 'end': '1997', 'start': '1993', 'education_org': "t' Schylger Jouw", 'summary': 'De school voor middelbaar algemeen voortgezet onderwijs (afgekort mavo) is een Nederlandse schoolsoort, volgens artikel 9 van de Wet op het voortgezet onderwijs, die werd ingevoerd in 1968, in de wandelgangen de Mammoetwet genoemd. Deze schoolsoort is de opvolger van de mulo, of ulo. Mavo 3 voor ulo (uitgebreid lager onderwijs) en mavo 4 voor mulo (meervoudig uitgebreid lager onderwijs). Sinds 1999 is de mavo vaak opgegaan in het voorbereidend middelbaar beroepsonderwijs (vmbo), waarbij het onderwijs wordt aangeboden als vmbo - theoretische leerweg.
 Mavo oude stijl had de volgende vakken:
 Nederlands
 Engels
 Wiskunde
 Natuurkunde
 Scheikunde
 Biologie
 Aardrijkskunde
 Tijdens het examenjaar deden de kandidaten naast de periodieke schoolonderzoeken het landelijke Centraal Examen, waarbij ze konden kiezen uit de moeilijkheidsniveaus C of D. Niveau D was hierbij het hoogste.'}]

[{'company_intern_id': 'shell', 'start': 'August 2005', 'job_title': 'Senior Operation Technician', 'description': "NAM’s mission is to sustainably (People, Planet, Profit) prospect for and produce oil and gas from deposits within the Netherlands and the Northsea.
 NAM is a joint venture of Shell (50%) and ExxonMobil (50%) with Shell as leading operator.

 Following the discovery of an oil field near Schoonebeek in 1943 by Exploratie Nederland, a Shell company, Shell and Esso decided to put up the capital jointly for a new oil exploration and production company: Nederlandse Aardolie Maatschappij, NAM was formed on 19 September 1947. It's logo represents the five cutters in a drill bit, seen from below.

 Development:
 NAM made the first natural gas discovery in the Netherlands in Coevorden in 1948. Just over ten years later, in 1959, NAM discovered the famous Groningen gas field near Slochteren, one of the biggest in the world, with original producible gas reserves of around 2,700 billion m³. That discovery also opened the door to offshore gas exploration and production, and in 1961 NAM was the first company in Western Europe to drill for gas in the North Sea.

 Today:
 NAM is now the largest gas producer in the Netherlands, with annual production of around 50 billion m³. A little over half of this gas (27 billion m³) comes from the Groningen field and the rest from various smaller fields elsewhere on the mainland (12.5 billion m³) and in the North Sea (11 billion m³). Gas produced by NAM covers around 75% of Dutch demand. NAM also continues to produce oil , around 0.4 million m³ a year.

 Future:
 NAM is working for the future. A good example is the underground gas storage facilities that NAM has constructed at Langelo and Grijpskerk, which enable us to meet demand even on the coldest days. Meanwhile, the search for new gas fields in the Netherlands and under the North Sea continues. On the basis of the currently proven reserves, NAM estimates that the Netherlands still has enough gas for about 25 years - depending, of course, on the rate of consumption", 'company_name': 'Shell Oil Company / Nederlandse Aardolie Maatschappij (NAM)'}, {'end': 'August 2005', 'company_intern_id': 'oceanwide_2', 'description': 'Oceanwide is a company who assignment workers to different compagnies as a recruiter

 During my time working for Oceanwide a was first recruited to Unocal (now know as ChervronTexaco) on different production facilities on the Dutch continental shelf. I worked as mechanical Proces Operator on the Horizon and Helm platform where oil and gas is produced.

 During my work I was responsible for the safety on board, the daily production of oil and gas and the quality of the overboard water, one of the waste in the proces.

 I tested wells on the test separator, take and analyze different types of samples from the oil, overboard water and biocide. I was also the responsible person for the safety systems like the electrical and diesel fire water pump. I was authorised to sign work permits as issuer and put safety systems in the override when needed for maintenance.
 I start and stop gas engines from caterpillar, gasturbines from Dresser Rand for power supply and I did also the maintenance on these equipment.
 I was responsible for the quality of the oil (water in oil ratio), quality of the overboard water (oil in water ratio) and also for the oil flow nominations.
 I was also responsible for the manifests of the helicopter and the supplyboat, and covered the function helicopter landing officer.

 Later on I switched my carriere to Centrica.
 I worked for Centrica on the J6A platform also in the Dutch Northsea.

 On this platform I was responsible for the gas and condensate (fluid hydrocarbons) flow nomination and the integrity of the platform. I operate the LM 1600 gasturbines from 12,5 MW with his Nuovo pignone centrifugal compressors (two gas trains), Solar centaur and Dresser Rand gasturbines for the electricity. I also send and receive scrapers on a daily base. On this platform I developed myself in trouble shooting in PLC programs, auxiliary cabinets and DCS system. We used here a DSC system from ABB. I operated from here 3 satellites, and one sub-sea well.', 'company_name': 'Oceanwide', 'start': 'August 2003', 'job_title': 'Process Operator'}, {'end': 'July 2002', 'company_intern_id': 'redwave', 'description': 'USG Energy is a company who assignment workers to different compagnies as a recruiter.

 During my stay with USG energy I worked as a Trainee on the jack-up rig Noble Al White. In this six months of my carriere I start as roustabout and worked as banksman on the rig. I was part off the helikopter team and later onn they send me to the drillfloor.
 On the Drillfloor I worked as Roughneck during drilling a gaswell on the K1-A platform ( owend bij Total) on the Dutch continental shelf. I learned a lot about the drilling techniques and give assisstence to the derrickman by making the drillingmud (oil and waterbased mud). I also operated the iron roughneck to connect drillpipe and drillcollars.', 'company_name': 'USG Energy', 'start': 'January 2002', 'job_title': 'Roughneck'}]

[{'company_intern_id': 'british-american-tobacco', 'start': 'November 2014', 'job_title': 'TaO Data Lead -Venezuela', 'description': 'Gestión de data por el EM de VE a nivel nacional e internacional a fin de adaptar lineamientos del Global and Regional Team para realizar la migración mundial de BAT a un ERP SAP que se adapte a las necesidades de todos los mercados de British American Tobacco. Para lograr el objetivo deseado, se ejecutaron las siguientes actividades a través de Work cycles:
 1.- Start up and Preparation: levantamiento de información, diseño del DATA MIGRATION INVENTORY (DMI) por area (Operaciones, Mercadeo y Finanzas) y General DMI.
 2.- Blue Print: Participación en el diseño y populado de documentos de mapeo (Map Documents) en los cuales se define el tipo de método a emplear para realizar el populado de la data (Transform, collect, Transform and Collect).
 3.- Realization: populado de Mapping tables y Collect load Templates para su Upload en la BDD de las aplicaciones globales a fin de garantizar la calidad de la data a migrar. Depuración de data a través de tres data Subcycle: DTL1, DTL3, RHL, validación de la data en cada uno de los Subcycle.

Já nos anos 80, ampliou seu portfólio de serviços e segmentos atendidos, passando a atuar também com o transporte de passageiros e terceirização de frotas. 

Na década seguinte, acompanhando a necessidade de seus clientes em reduzir custos, focou na otimização de suas cadeias de suprimentos, por meio da prestação de serviços dedicados e customizados.

Nos anos 2000, consolidou a prestação de serviços integrados de logística (Serviços Dedicados), principal fator que influenciou o crescimento da empresa nos últimos dez anos. Também realizou aquisições de empresas posicionadas em setores estratégicos da economia e adotou um sistema próprio de comercialização e renovação de frota, por meio de sua rede de lojas de veículos seminovos.

Em 2002, a JSL alcançou o primeiro lugar do ranking do transporte rodoviário no país em relação à receita líquida, ocupando a liderança absoluta no setor.', 'company_name': 'JSL S.A.', 'scraping_services_id': 6690163, 'size_min': 10001, 'industry': 'Logistics & Supply Chain'}

column7: [{'degrees': ['Mestrado em Engenharia Geotécnica e Geoambiente, Exploração e gestão sustentável dos recursos minerais, energéticos e hídricos.'], 'end': '2017', 'start': '2015', 'education_org': 'Instituto Superior de Engenharia do Porto', 'summary': 'Com o mestrado em Engenharia Geotécnica e Geoambiente, o ISEP especializa geo-profissionais com competências avançadas em geotecnia de rochas e solos, georrecursos, geotecnologias e ambiente. O curso está orientado para a inovação tecnológica dos setores extrativo, energético e ambiental, perspetivando também soluções para as grandes obras de engenharia.\n Concentrando-se no desenvolvimento de competências técnicas e científicas para a elaboração e coordenação de projetos geotécnicos, o plano de estudos integra unidades curriculares de geomecânica aplicada, escavações subterrâneas, tecnologias geoambientais, prospeção geotécnica e obras marítimas e fluviais. O mestrado aposta numa forte componente teórico-prática e experimental, combinando trabalhos de campo, a análise de estudos de caso, seminários com especialistas do setor e atividades laboratoriais e de investigação.'}, {'degrees': ['Licenciatura em Engenharia Geotécnica e Geoambiente, Engenharia Geotécnica'], 'end': '2015', 'start': '2011', 'education_org': 'Instituto Superior de Engenharia do Porto', 'summary': 'O plano de estudos desenvolve conhecimentos de física, geologia, desenho técnico, mecânica dos solos e gestão de projetos e aproveita a realização de trabalhos práticos para testar competências e estimular capacidades de raciocínio lógico, criatividade e de trabalho em equipa.'}, {'degrees': ['Ensino Secundário, Ciências e Tecnologias, Média - 16 valores'], 'end': '2011', 'start': '2005', 'education_org': 'Escola Basica e Secundária Ferreira de Castro', 'summary': 'Activities and Societies: -Banda de rock'}]
